HEADWORD: moniliasis
<hw>moniliasis</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>An infectious
disease caused by fungi of the genera
<causedby><gen>Monilia</gen></causedby> or
<causedby><gen>Candida</gen></causedby> especially
<causedby><spn>Candida albicans</spn></causedby>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> candidiasis, monilia disease.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

